OL,3,CFormer bishop pleads guilty to
OL,4,Chistoric sexual assault on boy
OL,6,FA former Bishop of Swansea and Brecon
OL,7,Fhas pleaded guilty to multiple counts
OL,8,Fof sexually abusing a child.
OL,10,FAnthony Pierce, 84, carried out the
OL,11,Fabuse in the 1980s whilst he was a
OL,12,Fparish priest in the West Cross area
OL,13,Fof Swansea.
OL,15,FPierce, who was bishop between 1999
OL,16,Fand 2008, pleaded guilty to five
OL,17,Fcounts of indecent assault on a boy
OL,18,Funder 16 years-of-age when he appeared
OL,19,Fat Swansea Crown Court.
