OL,6,FThe defendant of Coed Ceirios, Swansea
OL,7,FVale, is due to be sentenced on 7
OL,8,FMarch. He is currently on bail pending
OL,9,Fthe sentencing.
OL,11,FIn a statement the Church in Wales
OL,12,Fsaid allegations against the cleric
OL,13,Fcame to light in 2023 when the victim
OL,14,Fmade a disclosure to a Church in Wales
OL,15,Fsafeguarding officer. They said the
OL,16,Fdisclosure was then passed to the
OL,17,Fpolice.
