OL,6,FThe church said at the completion of
OL,7,Fthe criminal case the Church in Wales
OL,8,Fdisciplinary tribunal would consider
OL,9,F"further appropriate action" against
OL,10,FPierce.
OL,12,FIn the statement the church said: "We
OL,13,Facknowledge the bravery of the
OL,14,Fsurvivor in coming forward and thank
OL,15,Fthe police, Crown Prosecution Service
OL,16,Fand the local authority for their
OL,17,Fcareful work in this case.
