OL,6,F"The Church in Wales is appalled at
OL,7,Fthe offences which have been revealed
OL,8,Fin this case and expresses its deepest
OL,9,Fsympathy with the victim for the abuse
OL,10,Fthey have suffered.
OL,12,F"It is a cause of the most profound
OL,13,Fshame that a priest in the Church in
OL,14,FWales should have been convicted of
OL,15,Fsuch shocking crimes. Our prayers are
OL,16,Fwith the survivor and with all victims
OL,17,Fof abuse, whose welfare must always be
OL,18,Fat the heart of our work.
